> # Badge
> ## (Default: Off)
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>     No badge will be shown.
>
> * **On:**  
>     If the app has backgrounding enabled, a badge will be displayed on the app's icon on the home screen (SpringBoard).

- - -

> # Status Bar Icon
> ## (Default: Off)
> 
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>     No status bar icon will be shown.
>
> * **On:**  
>     If the app has backgrounding enabled, an icon will be displayed in the status bar when the app is the current app.
